<a name="toc_tc30230"></a><p>&nbsp;</p><div> <table class="tc" width="90%" ><tr><th colspan="4">Test Case P237-77: TC_VALID_SC_001&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 80%;">[Version  : 1]</span></th></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Author:</span></td><td colspan="3">vtir3660</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="4"><span class="label">Summary:</span><br /><p>1. Selecteaza reteta cu ID =1 (&quot;Reteta Cola&quot;)</p>

<p>2. Introdu in campul txtProdName valoarea &quot;Cola Premium&quot;</p>

<p>3. Introdu in campul txtProdPrice valoarea &quot;15.99&quot;</p>

<p>4. Verifica lista de produse existenta (trebuie sa fie fara coliziuni)</p>

<p>5. Apasa butonul&nbsp; de adaugare</p>
</td></tr><tr><td colspan="4"><span class="label">Preconditions:</span><br /><p>Aplicația este pornită, baza de date e accesibilă.</p>
</td></tr><tr><td><span class="label">#:</span></td><td><span class="label">Step actions:</span></td><td><span class="label">Expected Results:</span></td></tr><tr><td width="5">1</td><td><p>1. Selecteaza reteta cu ID =1 (&quot;Reteta Cola&quot;)</p>

<p>2. Introdu in campul txtProdName valoarea &quot;Cola Premium&quot;</p>

<p>3. Introdu in campul txtProdPrice valoarea &quot;15.99&quot;</p>

<p>4. Verifica lista de produse existenta (trebuie sa fie fara coliziuni)</p>

<p>5. Apasa butonul&nbsp; de adaugare</p>
</td><td><p>Produsul este creat cu succes; metoda service.addProduct() este apelată o dată; nodurile 1-6 sunt acoperite.</p>
</td></tr><tr><td width="5">2</td><td></td><td></td></tr><tr><td width="5">3</td><td></td><td></td></tr><tr><td width="5">4</td><td></td><td></td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Execution type:</span></td><td colspan="3">Manual</td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Estimated exec. duration (min):</span></td><td colspan="3"></td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Importance:</span></td><td colspan="3">Medium</td></tr>
